{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Transform"], "type": "title", "extent": [105, 119], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [119, 231], "text": ["The Transform operation transforms the source geometry in \"object space\" using a transformation matrix."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [231, 336], "text": ["The Transform operation transforms the source geometry in \"object space\" using a transformation matrix."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [336, 500], "text": ["All primitives selected will receive the same transform.  To vary the transform by a point attribute, use the ", {"text": ["Transform By Attribute SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/xformbyattrib", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/xformbyattrib"}, "."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [506, 628], "text": ["Vector VDBs will have their internal values transformed according\n    to the transform hint in their intrinsic data."]}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [628, 824], "text": ["SDF VDBs will not have their internal values updated, even if a uniform\n    scale is performed.  This can be done with a VDB Combine by setting\n    the A Multiply value to the scale amount."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "note", "extent": [500, 506]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "note_group"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [844, 882], "text": ["Subset of geometry to transform."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Group"], "role": "item", "extent": [836, 844], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [894, 951], "text": ["The type of elements referenced in the Group field."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Group Type"], "role": "item", "extent": [882, 894], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [968, 1011], "text": ["Order in which transformations occur."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Transform Order"], "role": "item", "extent": [951, 968], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1025, 1062], "text": ["Order in which rotations occur."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Rotate Order"], "role": "item", "extent": [1011, 1025], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1085, 1128], "text": ["Amount of translation along xyz axes."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Translate"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "t"}, "extent": [1062, 1073], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1148, 1188], "text": ["Amount of rotation about xyz axes."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Rotate"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "r"}, "extent": [1128, 1136], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1207, 1248], "text": ["Non-uniform scaling along xyz axes."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Scale"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "s"}, "extent": [1188, 1195], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1255, 1450], "text": ["Amount of shearing. The three values represent shearing in the\n    X direction on the XY plane, in the X direction on the XZ plane,\n    and in the Y direction on the YZ plane, respectively."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Shear"], "role": "item", "extent": [1248, 1255], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1469, 1513], "text": ["Local pivot point for transformations."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Pivot"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "p"}, "extent": [1450, 1457], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1544, 1566], "text": ["Uniform scaling."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Uniform Scale"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "scale"}, "extent": [1513, 1528], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1578, 1998], "text": ["These attributes are transformed, if they are marked as transforming.\n    Use ", {"text": ["Attribute Create"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/attribcreate", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/attribcreate"}, " to set the transformation type on an attribute to ", {"text": ["Position"], "type": "ui"}, ", ", {"text": ["Vector"], "type": "ui"}, ", ", {"text": ["Normal"], "type": "ui"}, ", ", {"text": ["Quaternion"], "type": "ui"}, ", or ", {"text": ["Transform Matrix"], "type": "ui"}, ". Set the type to ", {"text": ["None"], "type": "ui"}, " to make an attribute non-transforming, or\n    remove it from this list.  Primitive transforms are affected if and only if ", {"text": ["P"], "type": "code"}, " is transformed."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Attributes"], "role": "item", "extent": [1566, 1578], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2023, 2099], "text": ["Recomputes all normals as point normals, if a normal attribute exists."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Recompute Point Normals"], "role": "item", "extent": [1998, 2023], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2127, 2475], "text": ["Recomputes any normals that are affected by polygons that use both transformed and untransformed points. When transforming the full geometry or full connected components, the results should be the same as when this option is off, i.e. the normals will just be transformed and not recomputed. This does nothing if ", {"text": ["P"], "type": "code"}, " is not being transformed."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Recompute Affected Normals"], "role": "item", "extent": [2099, 2127], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2499, 2538], "text": ["Normal lengths remain unaffected."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Preserve Normal Length"], "role": "item", "extent": [2475, 2499], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2561, 2774], "text": ["Use the inverse of the transformation. This is the transformation which undoes the specified transformation. Two transform SOPs with all parameters but this equal will cancel out each other\u2019s transformation."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Invert Transformation"], "role": "item", "extent": [2538, 2561], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2825, 3120], "text": ["If this field is not blank, the node creates a ", {"text": ["detail"], "type": "em"}, " attribute with this\n        name, containing a 4\u00d74 matrix representing the applied transform. You can use\n        this, for example, to apply the same transform elsewhere, or reverse the\n        transformation later in the chain."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Output Attribute"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "outputattr"}, "extent": [2774, 2792], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [3159, 3470], "text": ["If the ", {"text": ["Output attribute"], "type": "ui"}, " already exists, this controls how/whether the node\n        combines the new transform with the existing one in the attribute.\n        \"Post-multiplication\" applies the transform in the same way as if you wired\n        multiple transform nodes to each other in the network."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Combine"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "combine"}, "extent": [3120, 3129], "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "extent": [824, 836], "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [3494, 3525], "text": ["The centroid of the input"]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [3478, 3494], "text": ["CEX, CEY, CEZ"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [3540, 3577], "text": ["The centroid of the input group"]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [3525, 3540], "text": ["GCX, GCY, GCZ"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [3589, 3641], "text": ["The X extents of the bounding box of the input"]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [3577, 3589], "text": ["XMIN, XMAX"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [3653, 3705], "text": ["The Y extents of the bounding box of the input"]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [3641, 3653], "text": ["YMIN, YMAX"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [3717, 3769], "text": ["The Z extents of the bounding box of the input"]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [3705, 3717], "text": ["ZMIN, ZMAX"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [3790, 3838], "text": ["The size of the bounding box of the input"]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [3769, 3790], "text": ["SIZEX, SIZEY, SIZEZ"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Locals", "role": "section", "extent": [3470, 3478], "container": true, "type": "locals_section", "id": "locals"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3847, 3866], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/edit", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/edit"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3866, 3884], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/peak", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/peak"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3884, 3907], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/primitive", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/primitive"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3907, 3926], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/point", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/point"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3926, 3949], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/softxform", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/softxform"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3949, 3972], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/xformaxis", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/xformaxis"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3972, 4000], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/xformbyattrib", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/xformbyattrib"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [3838, 3847], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["The Transform operation transforms the source geometry in \"object space\" using a transformation matrix."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": null, "tags": "transform, flip", "namespace": null, "bestbet": "transform", "internal": "xform", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "SOP/xform"}, "title": ["Transform"]}